---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 44
By: Eckhart
Tags:
  - Creation=Man’s Primordial Birthright
  - Life-Love=Love=God’s Love for Us
---
The plain truth is that of necessity God is bound to cherish us just as
though his Godhood were at stake, as in fact it is. God can no more do
without us than we can without him, nay, even if we turned from God it
would be impossible for God to turn his back on us.
